snippet.title: What's On Our Baby Registry
snippet.description:
Now that we know Baby Vaughn is a GIRL, we have completed our baby registry. We want to thank anyone in advance who wishes to bless us with something. We are so grateful that you even thought enough of us to support our growing family. We love you all and keep rocking with us! 

Baby Vaughn's Registry - https://www.target.com/gift-registry/gift/babyvaughncomingmarch

Brittney and Dorrie Vaughn 
P.O. Box 42822
OKC, OK 73123
